    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构建地牢布局，编写故事剧情，从海量自定义敌人中自由选择。大师模式将助您：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从零打造冒险内容，灵活运用现有资源与设定</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将冒险场景置入游戏世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他玩家共享冒险与挑战</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大师模式包含三大工具：地牢建造器、生物创造器与任务生成器。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地牢建造器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238570/extras/a5e31db567d02dc4c3ed8483e726a064.poster.avif?t=1764261050\" width=720 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238570/extras/a5e31db567d02dc4c3ed8483e726a064.webm?t=1764261050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238570/extras/a5e31db567d02dc4c3ed8483e726a064.mp4?t=1764261050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过地牢建造器，您可在地图特定位置创建地牢。无论是打造全新刺激的挑战，还是实现史诗级任务，您都能全面定制每个细节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此工具支持：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设定地牢深度及房间数量</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义每个房间</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >插入数十种不同敌人与战斗阵型，包括生物编辑器中创建的自定义生物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为玩家设定奖励与障碍</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造过程中将实时显示地牢的挑战值，该数值决定了对玩家的致命程度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地牢的生物群系将由其所在世界的区域决定。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生物创建器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238570/extras/076b8fdc6cde6c3dbce5bfea4c1a2f31.poster.avif?t=1764261050\" width=718 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238570/extras/076b8fdc6cde6c3dbce5bfea4c1a2f31.webm?t=1764261050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238570/extras/076b8fdc6cde6c3dbce5bfea4c1a2f31.mp4?t=1764261050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从埃隆達爾种族中选定一个，并按需进行定制。通过生物创建器编辑器，你可以修改所有参数、技能乃至战斗阵型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此工具支持：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择生物名称、描述及外观</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设定威胁等级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定制属性与抗性</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备技能并定义战斗风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建由自定义与经典生物组成的阵型</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到恰当的平衡点，将想象中的角色赋予生命，让他们在龙之秘境宇宙中活灵活现。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >任务构建器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238570/extras/e32fdfe929a13850f100c822b1e81f64.poster.avif?t=1764261050\" width=720 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238570/extras/e32fdfe929a13850f100c822b1e81f64.webm?t=1764261050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238570/extras/e32fdfe929a13850f100c822b1e81f64.mp4?t=1764261050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在任务构建器中，您可串联所有创作成果：地牢、角色与生物，共同演绎您构思的史诗级冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此工具可实现：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择任务起始的城市或世界区域</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构建任务各阶段流程</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过设定玩家行动路径定制每个阶段</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任务构建器能让你打造由任务与探索组成的完整冒险，将其他玩家带入你构想的龙之骑士世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在艾隆达尔世界创造新冒险轻而易举，我们确信这将带给你极大满足。创作内容将通过Steamworks直接共享，期待见证更多精彩故事在龙之秘境的奇幻世界中展开。</p>",
